title: Week 6 picks & Colts vs. Texans recap
itunes:title: Week 6 picks & Colts vs. Texans recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- preview every game on the Week 6 NFL slate and recap the Colts' 33-28 win over the Texans.
